### Upload provider post image to Supabase Storage
### Use multipart/form-data in REST Client that supports file uploads.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@providerId = REPLACE_PROVIDER_USER_ID

POST {{baseUrl}}/provider/uploads/post-image
x-user-id: {{providerId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----CodexBoundary

------CodexBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
------CodexBoundary--
